<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.2">
<l>nāṉmukaṉāḷ mikaittarukkai yirukku vāymai nalamikucī rurōmacaṉāl naviṟṟi nakkaṉ</l>
<l>ūṉmukamār talaiyōṭṭū ṇoḻitta ventai yoḷimalarccē vaṭiyaṇaivī ruḻucē yōṭac</l>
<l>cūṉmukamār vaḷaiyaḷaivā yukutta muttait tolkuruku ciṉaiyeṉac cūḻnti yaṅka</l>
<l>tēṉmukamār kamalavayal cēlpāy kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would touch the bright bud[-like], rosy feet of our father who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having revealed the pride of four-faced [Brahmā]</l>
<l rend="indent">about the quantity of his lifetime through Rōmacaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">[who had] great distinction in the quality of his recitation of the Ṛg,</l>
<l>Ending the food[alms] to the naked ascetic’s skull bowl</l>
<l rend="indent">covered in flesh from the face,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in Kāḻi where carp leap</l>
<l rend="indent">in paddy fields with lotuses with faces covered in nectar,</l>
<l>As, when the plough oxen run, adult birds wander, circling,</l>
<l rend="indent">as they think ‘[My] egg!’ about pearls which fall from the inside of clams</l>
<l rend="indent">which are full [as they] face pregnancy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
